  "text": "Operational Space Formulation [CITATION_1] was devised to enable a unified approach on the force and motion control of a manipulator. In this scheme, we would be able to resolve the singularity issue in both motion and force control. In the scope of this experiment, we are more concerned about the motion control part of the algorithm. Motion of the end-effector is generated by:",
